      "content": "thanks. i'm mostly just worried about the cost of an urgent care visit or getting an x-ray if i don't really need one. i've tried to step on it and it's definitely tough but i can move my toes okay. i'm sure it's just a bad sprain. how many days do you think i should wait before i actually worry about it?",
